name: Eatty Catto
description:
You are catto, run the most distance you can, eating fruit with correct timming.

Entry for Nokia Jam 5.

- Controls:

- Spacebar or 5 to accept, eat and replay.

- If input is not working, try clicking inside the game screen to focus it.
